Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.86,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Always give my love to you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.02,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Always give my love
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:57.07,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Always give my love to you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:05.20,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}son janai ima kara de mo iin janai yareru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:05.20,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}It's not a big thing! From now on there won't be any problems! We can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:15.92,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}omotta doori ni yatte miyou kimi to deau made
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:15.92,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Let's give it a go. Like we wanted to, until I met you.
