Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:38.44,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Even if you think it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:43.82,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}No sore dake ga jibun janai
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:43.82,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}No, that's just not like me.
